<note>
  <para>
    In <filename>Makefile.am</filename>:
  </para>

  <blockquote>
    <informalexample>
      <programlisting>
AM_CXXFLAGS=@STDTHREAD_CXXFLAGS@</programlisting>
    </informalexample>
  </blockquote>

  <para>
    <link linkend="ethreads"><function>&ns;::run</function>()</link> and
    <link linkend="msgdispatcherrun"><function>&ns;::start_threadmsgdispatcher</function>()</link>
    requires additional compilation flags for threading support added
    to the <filename>Makefile.am</filename>, from the
    <literal>@STDTHREAD_CXXFLAGS@</literal> which gets set up
    <link linkend="using">from <filename>configure.ac</filename></link>.
  </para>
</note>
